BEIJING, China, January 8, 2022/APO Group/ -- 
                                                        
                            On January 8, 2022, President Xi Jinping sent a message of sympathy to Mauritanian President Mohamed Ould Ghazouani over his infection with COVID-19.
                                I believe that under the leadership of President Ghazouani, Mauritania will surely defeat the pandemic at an early date
                            



